Text: Fantastic, I've been hunting for this book for years and didn't want to shell out lots of money because it's out of print - great job!  I am one happy lagomorph....

Tell Tale sells this on their website. If you want it printed as it was meant to be, buy it there. (I don't care enough so I just dl this file, but could be nice to know, right?)
